com.android.car.internal.util

类 BinderKeyValueContainer<K,V extends IInterface>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.android.car.internal.util.BinderKeyValueContainer<K,V>
  • 类型参数:
    K - type of the key of the item
    V - type wrapped in the value of the item

    public final class BinderKeyValueContainer<K,V extends IInterface>
extends java.lang.Object
    A map-like container to hold client's binder interface. The item in the container will be removed automatically once the associated binder is unlinked (dies).

    • 嵌套类概要

      嵌套类 
      限定符和类型 类和说明
      static interface  BinderKeyValueContainer.BinderDeathCallback<K>
      Interface to be implemented by object that wants to be notified whenever a binder is unlinked (dies).

        public void put(K key,
                V binderInterface)
        Adds the instance of IInterface representing the binder interface to this container.

        Internally, this binderInterface will be wrapped in a BinderInterfaceHolder when added.
